  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1236810/extras/b82b32e74df8a25ef7e81ed2e1316afc.poster.avif?t=1666386513\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1236810/extras/b82b32e74df8a25ef7e81ed2e1316afc.webm?t=1666386513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1236810/extras/b82b32e74df8a25ef7e81ed2e1316afc.mp4?t=1666386513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Controlling all axes of a drone without stabilization, <strong>it just can't be that hard, right?</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Crashing (a lot)</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1236810/extras/fe746d0e2db74bf03bfaae6dd4c88d73.poster.avif?t=1666386513\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1236810/extras/fe746d0e2db74bf03bfaae6dd4c88d73.webm?t=1666386513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1236810/extras/fe746d0e2db74bf03bfaae6dd4c88d73.mp4?t=1666386513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Brace-Brace! Drones will crash - almost guaranteed.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fly 'round</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1236810/extras/f7251802fd9213923e0b03b86a741c52.poster.avif?t=1666386513\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1236810/extras/f7251802fd9213923e0b03b86a741c52.webm?t=1666386513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1236810/extras/f7251802fd9213923e0b03b86a741c52.mp4?t=1666386513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Once you master it - enjoy a unique feel of flying.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Time Race your friends</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1236810/extras/a3823e7838e0c59a1fa25da3232447bd.poster.avif?t=1666386513\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1236810/extras/a3823e7838e0c59a1fa25da3232447bd.webm?t=1666386513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1236810/extras/a3823e7838e0c59a1fa25da3232447bd.mp4?t=1666386513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Of course there is a global leaderboard for every track, but also a short list to see how your friends are doing and challenge their LAP times. However, you probably won't make it past the tutorial or around a single LAP because it's insanely difficult. Turns out, all those \"drone pilots\" are probably couldn't handle a drone without stabilization.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Crash some more (a lot more)</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1236810/extras/66f41094f258bcb26480bcbed81847a3.poster.avif?t=1666386513\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1236810/extras/66f41094f258bcb26480bcbed81847a3.webm?t=1666386513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1236810/extras/66f41094f258bcb26480bcbed81847a3.mp4?t=1666386513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conclusion?</h2><strong>Hard2Fly is very, ... difficult</strong>",
